name: Humpday
description: Two guys take their bromance to another level when they participate in an art film project.

review.author: socarrasjorge
review.heading: Biggest cop-out ever
review.reviewBody: There was a lot of promise here, but ultimately the film is a huge cop out, which perhaps is the point. In this case an opportunity to perhaps delve a bit deeper into male friendship and men's more tender feelings for each other was squandered. Nothing lost, nothing gained.
